Smart cards contain a microprocessor that provides cryptographic functions and storage for signing keys and key parts. The 00JA710 and 00RY790 smart cards part is FIPS certified. Smart card readers from FC 0885 or FC 0891 can be carried forward. Smart cards can be used on TKE 10.0 with these readers. Access to and use of confidential data on the smart card are protected by a user-defined PIN. Up to 990 other smart cards can be ordered for backup. (The extra smart card feature code is FC 0900). When one feature code is ordered, 10 smart cards are included. The order increment is 1 - 99 (10 - 990 blank smart cards). If you are using Gemalto CT700 smart card readers:  MCA smart cards must be at the minimum applet version 0.4.
